data.description:
BEAUTIFUL A FRAME HOME OVERLOOKING STUNNING VIEW OF LAKE 
 Remodeled with mostly chemical free materials.

GARDEN LEVEL UNIT FOR POSSIBLE RENT/AIR BNB/MOTHER-IN-LAW SUITE/HOME OFFICE


1,125 square feet that includes large bonus room plus 40' X 10' patio, dedicated parking for potential renter/air bnb/other

ABOUT THE BONUS ROOM
It is 25 feet by 15 feet plus 9 X 9  L-shaped multi-purpose room. Carpeted with a large wall mirror. It has 1 large and 1 small closet.  It makes a perfect multi-purpose room, that could be used as a living room & as a media room. 

This absolutely stunning rental overlooks a private shimmering lake and a rolling golf course like lawn.  Located at the end of a private street in a good neighborhood.  The property is surrounded 360 degrees with trees, forest, and mountains. Wild life like deer and squirrels love to tantalize us with their beauty. Ideal reclusive, country hideaway, yet minutes from highway 280. 15 minutes to Arden; Brevard; 20 minutes to Fletcher; Hendersonville; 25 minutes to West Asheville. 

The inside has been custom designed. We have used non-toxic materials, such as, 0 VOC paint.   The carpet is 100% non-toxic. Real tongue-in-groove wood ceilings. Multi-color slate on the floor. The walls also have intricate stonework that enrich the ambiance. An archway with imported multi-color stone bridges the living room/office and dining room. There are 2 French doors with lake view, that open up to a large private patio approximately 10' X 40'. This is not an apartment. It is the lower level of a small estate-like home that walks out onto the patio overlooking a rolling lawn and lake. Neighbors live at a discreet distance offering you complete privacy. 

1 bedroom, large Bonus room, 1 small bathroom, living room, dining room and an efficiency kitchen. There is a large long L-shaped counter with lots of storage cabinets.  There is an area to grow an organic vegetable/herb garden. Washer and dryer. There are 2 closet spaces, a small utility closet and generous shelf storage in the bathroom.  If you have a lot of 'stuff', you will need to rent a storage unit as there is no place to accommodate storage items.  Rental is in mint condition and move in date is asap.  No pets preferred
(However pet parents willing to pay a one time pet fee for each pet may apply.  Then, 1 or 2 quiet, well trained, continent pets are acceptable).  Indoor cats must be trained to use the scratching post, not the carpet.  

We need to meet all occupants including pets before renting.  Thanks.
Good credit and rental history, verifiable monthly income from employment or retirement benefits that will ensure you can cover the rent plus utilities comfortably, is required to qualify.

CALL Kash or Chuck 828 393 5955 Rent is $850 plus utilities which is less than half of whole house. Security deposit $1150.  Pet fee.  House is a duplex but very private, separate entrances, separate parking, quiet, end of street.
data.whatILove:
Stonework, arches, stunning lake view, 360 degrees of mountains, forest, meadows & wild life.  A lot of windows facing the sun.  Vaulted ceilings.
Potential Air BnB/vacation rental income or mother in law suite.  3 large rooms for working out/game room etc.  Easy access to Brevard, Hendersonville, Asheville.
